WEBVTT

00:17.000 --> 00:18.000
HAVE A FULL MEAL

00:18.080 --> 00:18.760
Damn it.

00:18.840 --> 00:20.040
Finally got it.

00:20.120 --> 00:21.160
All right.

00:21.240 --> 00:23.000
-Let's go.
-Stop.

00:28.120 --> 00:29.720
-Where did this one come from?
-Did you see him?

00:29.800 --> 00:30.800
You didn't notice him?

00:36.720 --> 00:37.880
Hand over the deed,

00:37.960 --> 00:39.640
then I'll let you go.

00:51.640 --> 00:52.640
I refuse.

00:53.920 --> 00:55.880
I'll stride straight out of here.

00:56.400 --> 00:58.120
If you can, try and stop me.

01:07.560 --> 01:09.680
You bunch of damned scoundrels.

01:09.760 --> 01:11.480
Put it down, now!

01:19.880 --> 01:23.720
You bunch of neighbors
are really interesting.

01:23.800 --> 01:25.440
You're all courting death, are you?

01:25.520 --> 01:26.520
If you want to leave,

01:26.600 --> 01:30.080
ask my broom if it'll allow it!

01:40.840 --> 01:42.040
Get over here.

01:42.120 --> 01:43.120
Get over here!

01:43.800 --> 01:44.720
You old man!

01:44.800 --> 01:46.600
Run, and I'll chase you down!

01:46.680 --> 01:47.680
Wait a minute.

01:48.320 --> 01:49.640
Sir.

02:01.560 --> 02:03.040
Let's see you run!

02:03.120 --> 02:04.360
Let's see you run!

02:05.440 --> 02:07.560
-Are you okay?
-I'm not.

02:13.000 --> 02:13.840
You dare hit me?

02:13.920 --> 02:15.280
You've got it coming!

02:15.360 --> 02:16.960
Damn you!

02:17.040 --> 02:19.040
Damn you!

02:19.880 --> 02:21.760
Damn you!

02:21.840 --> 02:24.560
Fists don't have eyes.
Quick, find a place to hide!

02:34.960 --> 02:35.880
Stinky old man.

02:47.000 --> 02:47.840
Hey! Hey!

02:47.920 --> 02:49.120
That's enough!

02:53.160 --> 02:55.720
Damn you! Damn you!

02:56.240 --> 02:57.280
Changyu!

02:57.360 --> 02:58.360
Changyu, quickly!

02:59.400 --> 03:01.800
-Madam Zhuang, please look after Ning.
-Okay.

03:16.200 --> 03:18.040
Take this!

03:32.680 --> 03:34.160
Ms. Fan, listen to me!

03:40.360 --> 03:41.320
Let me see who dares!

03:49.520 --> 03:51.440
Quick, quick, quick!

03:51.520 --> 03:53.920
Changyu, don't fight anymore.

03:54.440 --> 03:56.600
Old Zhao has nearly beaten them to death.

03:56.680 --> 03:58.880
If you strike again, they'll die.

04:02.600 --> 04:04.160
Didn't learn your lesson, huh?

04:05.280 --> 04:06.440
Ms. Fan.

04:06.520 --> 04:07.640
Your Ladyship, Ms. Fan.

04:08.360 --> 04:09.200
You've misunderstood.

04:09.800 --> 04:10.960
We came this time

04:12.080 --> 04:14.280
because we heard you're getting married.
We're here to congratulate you.

04:14.360 --> 04:16.399
Yes, yes, yes! We…
We came to congratulate you.

04:16.480 --> 04:18.160
We're not here to take the title deed.

04:20.800 --> 04:23.360
You came to congratulate
armed with weapons?

04:24.280 --> 04:26.280
My husband is already injured,

04:26.360 --> 04:28.160
and you few still beat him up!

04:28.680 --> 04:29.520
No, no, no!

04:29.600 --> 04:30.560
-We didn't!
-We didn't.

04:30.640 --> 04:32.080
We didn't lay a finger on him.

04:32.160 --> 04:33.760
-Didn't… Didn't hurt him.
-No.

04:38.520 --> 04:39.360
He got scared.

04:40.400 --> 04:41.600
That's no better!

04:41.680 --> 04:43.160
Don't, don't, don't!

04:50.360 --> 04:52.960
So, this gentleman
is your esteemed husband?

04:53.480 --> 04:54.920
We didn't realize who he was.

04:55.000 --> 04:56.160
We didn't realize who he was.

04:56.240 --> 04:57.240
Money. The money.

04:59.480 --> 05:00.920
We really came to congratulate you.

05:01.000 --> 05:02.040
Congratulations.

05:05.480 --> 05:06.640
Have mercy on us.

05:07.800 --> 05:08.640
That's all.

05:09.600 --> 05:10.600
Have mercy on us.

05:10.680 --> 05:12.040
Get out, now.

05:12.880 --> 05:13.920
If you dare come again,

05:14.560 --> 05:16.040
we will beat you to death.

05:17.440 --> 05:18.800
Come on. Let's go.

05:20.600 --> 05:21.920
-Get the hell out!
-Go away!

05:22.000 --> 05:22.840
Move!

05:22.920 --> 05:23.880
-Well done!
-Well done!

05:26.320 --> 05:27.640
Are you okay?

05:29.120 --> 05:30.800
They did hurt you.

05:31.680 --> 05:33.240
-I'll go kill them.
-It's not them.

05:34.400 --> 05:36.080
-Then whose fault is it?
-Mine.

05:37.600 --> 05:38.840
I sat on him.

05:38.920 --> 05:39.800
So did I!

05:39.880 --> 05:41.600
-Me, too.
-Me, too.

05:45.160 --> 05:46.080
-Right.
-Come.

05:46.160 --> 05:47.920
-We're here. Be careful.
-Make way.

05:48.880 --> 05:51.840
It's all Old Zhao's fault
for being clumsy.

05:51.920 --> 05:53.040
I just went to buy groceries.

05:53.120 --> 05:54.920
You nearly crushed him sitting on him.

05:55.000 --> 05:56.320
He just recovered.

05:56.920 --> 05:58.280
Good thing Mr. Zhao stepped in.

05:58.360 --> 05:59.360
I can't thank you enough.

06:00.280 --> 06:02.120
Mrs. Zhao, you all go rest.

06:02.200 --> 06:03.400
I'll take care of Yan Zheng.

06:03.480 --> 06:04.360
Alright.

06:04.440 --> 06:07.000
-I'll cook to thank everyone.
-Alright.

06:07.080 --> 06:07.920
-Let's go.
-Come on.

06:08.000 --> 06:09.000
Go outside.

06:10.400 --> 06:12.600
Yan Zheng, give me your hand.

06:14.840 --> 06:16.280
Old Zhao, come out.

06:16.880 --> 06:17.720
What?

06:18.320 --> 06:19.520
What do you think?

06:19.600 --> 06:21.920
-I haven't even checked his pulse yet.
-What?

06:22.000 --> 06:22.960
Can't you take a hint?

06:23.040 --> 06:24.600
What hint?

06:38.320 --> 06:40.200
The wound on your back has split open.

06:40.720 --> 06:42.280
There's a large bloodstain.

06:42.800 --> 06:44.040
I need to clean it.

06:44.120 --> 06:45.760
I'll do it myself.

06:45.840 --> 06:46.720
Let me help.

06:58.560 --> 07:00.640
You were the one who did it, weren't you?

07:02.160 --> 07:03.520
This wound of yours,

07:03.600 --> 07:05.000
even if Uncle pressed on it,

07:05.080 --> 07:06.960
wouldn't have split open like this.

07:08.160 --> 07:09.320
You got into a fight.

07:10.680 --> 07:11.760
From your build,

07:12.360 --> 07:13.640
I can tell

07:15.280 --> 07:16.640
you're trained in martial arts.

07:30.000 --> 07:31.280
I was an armed escort,

07:31.840 --> 07:33.360
traveling north and south.

07:34.080 --> 07:35.760
It's just for protection.

07:36.280 --> 07:38.240
I didn't intentionally hide it from you.

07:42.640 --> 07:43.720
No wonder.

07:44.720 --> 07:46.640
My father was also an armed escort before.

07:46.720 --> 07:49.080
He also had many old scars
like yours on his body.

07:49.160 --> 07:50.360
Being an escort

07:50.440 --> 07:52.920
means gambling with your life.

07:57.560 --> 07:58.640
Bear with it.

08:02.360 --> 08:03.600
At Hucha Pass,

08:04.120 --> 08:06.360
you also encountered bandits
and got injured in the fight?

08:11.360 --> 08:12.520
Yes.

08:15.440 --> 08:17.440
There's nothing of value here.

08:17.520 --> 08:18.960
If they want to smash, let them.

08:19.040 --> 08:20.160
Why did you take action?

08:22.480 --> 08:23.920
If I didn't take action,

08:25.280 --> 08:26.760
they would have taken this.

08:32.720 --> 08:36.120
DEED OF CONDITIONAL SALE

08:52.240 --> 08:55.320
You did it for this title deed?

09:24.440 --> 09:25.320
Thank you.

10:57.680 --> 11:02.360
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL ZHU YU
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

11:06.120 --> 11:08.680
With this broom of mine today,

11:08.760 --> 11:10.080
they all fell down.

11:10.640 --> 11:13.080
Just touch someone, and they fall.

11:13.600 --> 11:16.520
No wonder they say
even a rabbit bites when cornered.

11:16.600 --> 11:17.800
If not for these fights,

11:17.880 --> 11:19.200
I wouldn't have known I'm so capable.

11:19.280 --> 11:20.280
Of course.

11:20.800 --> 11:23.080
We are the War Gods of Xigu Alley.

11:23.160 --> 11:24.800
-Right, come on, come on.
-That's right.

11:24.880 --> 11:25.960
Have a drink.

11:26.040 --> 11:27.280
Drink up, drink up.

11:30.360 --> 11:33.320
I say, we're no worse
than that Marquis Wu'an.

11:33.400 --> 11:35.440
-Right?
-Of course.

11:36.800 --> 11:37.840
Of course.

11:40.720 --> 11:41.560
However,

11:42.160 --> 11:44.280
you, young man, are a bit weak.

11:44.360 --> 11:46.680
Getting injured just from me
sitting on you.

11:47.200 --> 11:49.520
Changyu, be sure to nourish him well.

11:51.080 --> 11:51.920
Mr. Zhao,

11:52.000 --> 11:53.640
his old injuries haven't healed yet.

11:54.280 --> 11:56.280
Come, let's have a drink, man to man.

11:57.480 --> 12:00.600
Don't drink alcohol. Have tea.

12:00.680 --> 12:02.480
So protective of your husband, are you?

12:02.560 --> 12:05.720
Drinking a little alcohol is okay.
It promotes blood circulation.

12:06.240 --> 12:07.160
Old Zhao,

12:07.240 --> 12:08.760
what are you stirring up here?

12:08.840 --> 12:11.480
He's only just recovered.
How could he drink? He's not like you.

12:11.560 --> 12:13.000
-Go.
-Old Zhao, come here to drink.

12:13.080 --> 12:13.920
Let's drink.

12:14.000 --> 12:16.840
Changyu, did Fan Daniu
really submit the petition?

12:17.680 --> 12:18.840
Is he really that shameless?

12:22.120 --> 12:24.200
Then how about hiring a petition writer?

12:24.720 --> 12:26.560
It would cost so much
to hire a petition writer.

12:26.640 --> 12:27.960
Then what should we do?

12:28.960 --> 12:31.240
How about talking to Song Yan?

12:32.200 --> 12:34.920
After all, he's the only scholar
in our Xigu Alley.

12:35.000 --> 12:37.680
A provincial graduate
doesn't even kneel before officials.

12:37.760 --> 12:40.240
He can surely help Changyu with her case.

12:40.320 --> 12:42.720
Changyu won't ask a bad person for help.

12:43.800 --> 12:44.760
Ning is right.

12:44.840 --> 12:45.840
We won't go begging that ungrateful snake.

12:45.920 --> 12:48.160
Right,
we won't mention that ungrateful snake.

12:48.240 --> 12:49.720
Come on, come on. Drink, drink.

12:49.800 --> 12:51.240
Come, brothers, down it.

12:51.760 --> 12:52.920
-Drink.
-Come on.

12:53.000 --> 12:54.120
Now this is good wine.

12:54.200 --> 12:55.120
Don't worry.

12:55.640 --> 12:56.760
I'll help you.

12:58.120 --> 12:58.960
You?

12:59.040 --> 13:01.320
XIGU ALLEY

13:08.480 --> 13:09.400
That's all.

13:09.480 --> 13:11.160
My mother used them before.

13:11.240 --> 13:12.400
Make do with them.

13:14.000 --> 13:15.000
I'll write down

13:15.080 --> 13:17.000
the response procedure
and the legal phrasing.

13:17.080 --> 13:18.760
Memorize them later.

13:18.840 --> 13:21.400
Once in court, you'll naturally pass.

13:22.040 --> 13:23.760
You can write?

13:23.840 --> 13:24.880
You know these things?

13:25.480 --> 13:27.800
I've traveled far and wide.
You learn a thing or two.

13:40.280 --> 13:41.520
What's wrong?

13:44.360 --> 13:45.880
Before, I thought

13:46.400 --> 13:49.320
Song Yan was the most
amazing person in the world.

13:49.400 --> 13:51.040
I didn't expect you to be better.

13:51.120 --> 13:53.920
Not only do you know martial arts,
but you can also write essays.

13:57.080 --> 13:58.440
The provincial graduate

13:58.520 --> 14:00.440
who wouldn't come out to help you

14:00.960 --> 14:02.560
even when Mrs. Zhao
shouted herself hoarse?

14:04.720 --> 14:06.760
How about you go to court for me instead?

14:06.840 --> 14:08.280
According to the Dayin Code,

14:08.800 --> 14:10.680
only the head of the house
can go to court.

14:11.440 --> 14:13.520
I'm not the head of the house,
so I can't go to court.

14:14.440 --> 14:17.080
Isn't this like forcing a duck
onto a perch?

14:19.200 --> 14:20.800
-Changyu.
-It's my turn.

14:20.880 --> 14:21.920
Silence!

14:23.880 --> 14:26.080
Who is this below the dais
and for what matter?

14:26.600 --> 14:27.640
State your case.

14:28.640 --> 14:29.800
How imposing.

14:29.880 --> 14:31.200
How imposing.

14:38.200 --> 14:40.200
Your Honor,

14:40.960 --> 14:42.240
my name is Fan Changyu.

14:42.760 --> 14:44.160
I am here for the matter

14:44.240 --> 14:45.080
of my house.

14:45.920 --> 14:47.640
-Are your parents present?
-Both deceased.

14:48.360 --> 14:49.400
Based on the Dayin Code,

14:49.920 --> 14:52.120
a house without a male heir
goes to the closest relative.

14:52.200 --> 14:54.440
-If one brother dies, the other--
-Nonsense!

14:55.040 --> 14:56.520
Nonsense!

14:58.800 --> 15:00.480
Disrupting the court! Ning,

15:01.520 --> 15:03.400
-ten heavy strokes of the board.
-Okay.

15:05.040 --> 15:06.040
One, two…

15:06.720 --> 15:07.840
You're serious?

15:11.360 --> 15:12.840
Your Honor,

15:13.960 --> 15:15.240
according to the Dayin Code,

15:15.960 --> 15:17.960
Section on Inheritance, Egg 17,

15:18.840 --> 15:19.960
when the household is egg,

15:20.040 --> 15:21.840
-you must choose an egg.
-Stop.

15:21.920 --> 15:22.760
Egg…

15:22.840 --> 15:24.720
What egg are you talking about?

15:27.160 --> 15:28.680
I never remember the characters.

15:28.760 --> 15:30.800
My mother said when I can't recall one,

15:30.880 --> 15:31.840
just draw an egg.

15:31.920 --> 15:32.960
I got used to saying it.

15:33.040 --> 15:34.680
WHEN A HOUSEHOLD HAS NO HEIR,
ONE MUST BE CHOSEN.

15:36.120 --> 15:37.800
I really can't remember.

15:37.880 --> 15:39.080
How about this?

15:39.960 --> 15:42.600
We find a sack and tie up Fan Daniu.
What do you say?

15:44.320 --> 15:46.560
-And then?
-Mr. Wang said

15:46.640 --> 15:48.360
if he's not present when the court opens,

15:48.440 --> 15:49.800
the case is invalid.

15:57.120 --> 15:58.640
Having gotten away with it once,

15:58.720 --> 16:00.400
there will be a next time.

16:01.000 --> 16:01.920
It can be a good idea

16:02.560 --> 16:04.000
to kill him directly.

16:06.440 --> 16:08.080
End it once and for all. What do you say?

16:13.280 --> 16:16.400
Kill… Killing is against the law!

16:17.080 --> 16:18.080
Let's… Let's not.

16:22.360 --> 16:23.840
Since you can't be that ruthless,

16:24.360 --> 16:26.040
then you'll have to suffer yourself.

16:26.120 --> 16:27.040
Continue memorizing.

16:30.400 --> 16:33.040
Dayin Code, Household Ordinance,
Extinction Chapter,

16:33.560 --> 16:34.480
Article 17,

16:35.120 --> 16:37.120
or a household that is extinc…

16:40.040 --> 16:41.680
Don't be mad.

16:41.760 --> 16:43.160
Your health matters.

16:43.240 --> 16:44.280
I'll keep memorizing.

16:44.880 --> 16:45.720
Forget it.

16:47.040 --> 16:48.360
Recite the Seven-Step Poem.

16:48.440 --> 16:50.720
I suppose the law also follows reason.

16:50.800 --> 16:53.360
Perhaps this can move the magistrate more.

16:54.040 --> 16:56.880
Magistrate Cui also passed
both imperial exams.

16:58.120 --> 16:59.000
What poem?

17:00.920 --> 17:02.120
Pods burned to cook peas

17:02.200 --> 17:03.560
Peas weep in the pot

17:03.640 --> 17:04.920
Grown from the same root

17:05.000 --> 17:06.240
Why torment each other?

17:06.319 --> 17:07.119
What does it mean?

17:07.720 --> 17:10.200
It means boiling beans
uses beanstalks as firewood.

17:10.720 --> 17:12.920
It means a life-and-death struggle
between brothers.

17:13.000 --> 17:16.359
It also refers to Fan Daniu
oppressing his nieces,

17:16.440 --> 17:17.280
being heartless.

17:18.040 --> 17:19.319
Brilliant.

17:21.800 --> 17:24.280
This poem was written
for Fan Daniu, wasn't it?

17:24.359 --> 17:26.119
He's hardly worthy of it.

17:30.720 --> 17:32.480
-What does fu mean?
-Pot.

17:34.080 --> 17:37.040
Same root probably means
having the same father.

17:38.440 --> 17:39.640
Then what about Xiangjian?

17:40.160 --> 17:42.000
Is it a way to cook vegetables?

17:42.080 --> 17:44.160
It's a metaphorical way
to say kill each other.

17:48.280 --> 17:49.440
Got it.

17:50.520 --> 17:51.680
Really?

17:56.840 --> 17:59.320
Boil beans, burn beanstalks.

18:00.360 --> 18:01.560
The beans in the pot…

18:02.880 --> 18:04.320
cry out.

18:05.400 --> 18:07.680
We share the same father.

18:07.760 --> 18:10.360
Why kill me first?

18:17.440 --> 18:18.280
That's not right.

18:21.360 --> 18:22.720
I can't say it's wrong either.

18:24.280 --> 18:25.720
Your Honor!

18:25.800 --> 18:28.160
Your Honor!

18:32.200 --> 18:35.040
Boil beans, burn beanstalks.

18:35.120 --> 18:37.400
The beans in the pot cry out.

18:37.920 --> 18:40.080
We share the same father.

18:40.160 --> 18:42.720
Why kill me first?

18:54.520 --> 18:55.480
XIGU ALLEY

18:55.560 --> 18:57.960
Boil beans, burn beanstalks.

18:58.040 --> 19:00.400
The beans in the pot cry out.

19:01.040 --> 19:03.800
We share the same father.

19:03.880 --> 19:07.240
Why kill me first?

19:08.520 --> 19:11.240
Your Honor!

19:11.320 --> 19:15.920
Your Honor!

19:17.560 --> 19:20.120
Your Honor!

19:22.120 --> 19:24.760
WINTER FADES AND SPRING RETURNS
TO BLESS THE LAND

19:28.760 --> 19:30.720
Yan, where are you going?

19:33.920 --> 19:35.760
I am just tired from studying.

19:35.840 --> 19:37.200
I want to go out for a walk.

19:46.360 --> 19:49.880
You still have the metropolitan
and palace exams ahead.

19:51.280 --> 19:53.480
Don't do anything rash.

19:58.600 --> 19:59.440
I know.

20:08.480 --> 20:10.720
Boil beans…

21:01.600 --> 21:02.480
Mother.

21:08.840 --> 21:09.880
Mother.

21:12.040 --> 21:13.200
I'm so tired.

22:02.600 --> 22:03.720
Did I disturb you?

22:03.800 --> 22:06.440
I just fell asleep
using your hand as a pillow.

22:11.440 --> 22:13.640
You also got sleepy from reading, right?

22:15.400 --> 22:16.760
I understand that.

22:20.880 --> 22:21.920
Why did the lamp go out?

22:22.000 --> 22:23.600
I'll go find a fire starter.

22:26.040 --> 22:27.880
Who's knocking so late at night?

22:33.320 --> 22:35.320
Song Yan, why are you here?

22:35.400 --> 22:36.440
Let me in first.

22:36.520 --> 22:37.680
Don't let my mother see.

22:38.720 --> 22:39.760
I have…

22:41.280 --> 22:42.160
What?

22:50.880 --> 22:51.720
Changyu.

22:52.320 --> 22:54.800
I came risking the great crime
of defying my elders

22:54.880 --> 22:55.760
to help keep the home.

22:57.160 --> 22:58.000
What?

22:58.760 --> 23:00.760
I thought for a long time these past days.

23:00.840 --> 23:02.480
I finally thought of a way.

23:04.320 --> 23:06.080
I came to tell you

23:06.160 --> 23:07.800
I will take you as my concubine.

23:13.720 --> 23:15.520
Has a donkey kicked you in the head?

23:15.600 --> 23:16.880
Don't celebrate too soon.

23:16.960 --> 23:19.640
I can only try to beg the magistrate
to do me a special favor.

23:20.440 --> 23:22.160
With my status as a provincial graduate,

23:22.240 --> 23:23.920
the magistrate may grant it.

23:24.000 --> 23:26.520
This way, you can keep your home

23:26.600 --> 23:28.440
and get the status you wish for.

23:30.760 --> 23:31.840
Song Yan.

23:32.720 --> 23:34.640
You think by stooping to take

23:34.720 --> 23:36.760
a pig-slaughtering woman like me
as your concubine,

23:37.280 --> 23:38.840
I should be grateful?

23:39.480 --> 23:40.960
I didn't think that.

23:41.560 --> 23:44.760
It's just, I never expected
that for this house,

23:44.840 --> 23:46.480
you would act so impulsively,

23:46.560 --> 23:48.760
giving yourself to a crippled refugee
from Chongzhou.

23:48.840 --> 23:50.800
-A crippled refugee?
-Yes.

23:53.200 --> 23:55.120
Song Yan, I'm really curious.

23:56.240 --> 23:57.800
What makes you look down on him?

23:58.520 --> 24:00.800
He is good at literary and martial arts,
educated and sensible.

24:00.880 --> 24:02.920
In terms of looks,
he's ten times better than you.

24:03.520 --> 24:04.600
Most importantly,

24:05.320 --> 24:06.640
he knows gratitude.

24:07.160 --> 24:08.760
He understands my difficulties.

24:08.840 --> 24:10.400
He's willing to marry into my family.

24:11.280 --> 24:12.720
In my time of crisis,

24:12.800 --> 24:14.440
even though he was injured,

24:14.960 --> 24:16.320
he still helped me seek justice.

24:16.920 --> 24:18.160
Such affection and loyalty

24:19.040 --> 24:20.440
is many times better than yours.

24:21.720 --> 24:24.520
You're just unwilling to accept it now

24:25.240 --> 24:27.600
and want to gain a good reputation
among the neighbors.

24:28.120 --> 24:30.520
That's why you're forced
to come knocking, Song Yan.

24:31.160 --> 24:32.560
You want your hand

24:33.080 --> 24:34.760
in every good thing.

24:34.840 --> 24:35.680
It's not like that.

24:35.760 --> 24:37.360
I truly care for you.

24:37.960 --> 24:40.040
I, Song Yan, now take your hand and swear…

24:43.200 --> 24:44.040
I…

24:46.400 --> 24:48.360
‎BE KIND, DO GOOD

24:48.440 --> 24:49.680
Who are you?

24:50.200 --> 24:51.720
Who am I?

24:57.360 --> 24:58.520
A crippled refugee.

25:03.960 --> 25:05.320
I worry about you every night,

25:06.080 --> 25:07.680
yet you are so unfaithful!

25:07.760 --> 25:09.200
Who are you to me?

25:09.280 --> 25:10.240
Unfaithful to whom?

25:11.160 --> 25:12.680
You disregard propriety and honor.

25:12.760 --> 25:14.680
Simply depraved and corrupting morals!

25:14.760 --> 25:15.880
Based on the Dayin Code,

25:15.960 --> 25:17.200
adultery carries 80 strokes!

25:17.280 --> 25:18.920
Based on the Dayin Code,

25:19.000 --> 25:21.280
breaking in at night makes you a thief.

25:21.360 --> 25:22.920
Serves you right to be beaten to death.

25:23.000 --> 25:24.440
Don't look away.

25:27.440 --> 25:29.000
He is my husband.

25:29.800 --> 25:32.440
Fan Changyu's rightful and legitimate man.

25:37.760 --> 25:38.880
You…

25:38.960 --> 25:40.280
You bring shame upon people.

25:40.360 --> 25:42.120
You bring shame upon people!

25:42.880 --> 25:45.800
To actually commit
such defiling and corrupting acts…

25:46.320 --> 25:47.480
Simply corrupting morals.

26:05.920 --> 26:07.920
Why did I kiss him?

26:08.880 --> 26:11.480
If I scared him off from marrying in,

26:12.680 --> 26:15.640
wouldn't that be gaining a small advantage
but suffering a big loss?

26:18.840 --> 26:22.360
THE HUNDRED HORSES

26:40.960 --> 26:42.520
It's all damn Song Yan's fault.

26:44.160 --> 26:45.360
Damn Song Yan.

26:46.240 --> 26:48.400
Damn Song Yan, Damn Song Yan.

26:59.360 --> 27:01.320
What on earth is that woman thinking?

27:02.600 --> 27:04.480
Just for such a lousy live-in husband?

27:04.560 --> 27:06.360
VIRTUE ALONE ENNOBLES

27:06.440 --> 27:08.640
SPRING BREEZE TOFU SHOP

27:08.720 --> 27:09.680
Miss.

27:20.800 --> 27:22.800
Mrs. Zhao, where's Mr. Zhao?

27:22.880 --> 27:24.000
He went to the town.

27:33.960 --> 27:35.120
Mr. Zhao, you're back.

27:35.800 --> 27:37.840
Mrs. Zhao, I've got things to do.
I need to go.

27:38.920 --> 27:40.200
-Changyu.
-Mr. Zhao.

27:44.200 --> 27:47.960
Why does this young couple
seem to be avoiding each other?

27:48.560 --> 27:51.200
Young brides get nervous before marriage.

27:51.280 --> 27:53.280
Although Changyu has a boyish personality,

27:53.360 --> 27:54.520
she will also be shy.

27:55.360 --> 27:57.080
You were also shy before marrying me.

27:57.160 --> 27:58.480
Shy?

27:58.560 --> 28:00.680
-I cried so much, I was so regretful.
-Look at you.

28:01.400 --> 28:02.240
Yan Zheng.

28:02.320 --> 28:04.440
Yan Zheng, you're awake.

28:05.040 --> 28:06.240
Changyu went to the town.

28:06.320 --> 28:07.160
I know.

28:08.200 --> 28:09.400
I need to talk to you, Mr. Zhao.

28:09.480 --> 28:11.640
Perfect. I was also looking for you. Come.

28:11.720 --> 28:12.560
Come.

28:13.360 --> 28:14.440
Be careful.

28:16.560 --> 28:18.520
That essay, or whatever you wrote,

28:19.280 --> 28:21.000
can sell for that much money?

28:22.400 --> 28:23.480
Is this a lot?

28:23.560 --> 28:25.680
Twenty taels isn't a lot?

28:25.760 --> 28:29.080
I thought the bookstore owner was crazy.

28:30.920 --> 28:33.680
WU AND QI HAVE ARRIVED
AT LIN'AN'S FOUR SEASONS BOOKSHOP

28:33.760 --> 28:36.320
What kind of genius stuff are you writing?

28:39.080 --> 28:41.200
I've traveled a lot and seen much.

28:41.280 --> 28:43.280
I can whip up something to bluff them.

28:43.800 --> 28:46.840
Didn't expect the bookstore owner
to actually accept it.

28:47.640 --> 28:50.120
That's all profit, no cost.

28:50.200 --> 28:52.000
Write a few more.
I will help you sell them.

28:53.960 --> 28:55.960
These are all imitations
of masters' works.

28:56.040 --> 28:58.120
Writing too many might expose the trick.

28:58.200 --> 28:59.280
Not advisable.

29:00.840 --> 29:03.160
Right. We should keep it on the down-low.

29:03.680 --> 29:05.480
But writing like this occasionally

29:05.560 --> 29:06.920
is enough for a year's expenses.

29:09.160 --> 29:11.360
This little money is enough
for a whole year?

29:12.000 --> 29:14.000
For a small family,

29:14.080 --> 29:15.800
if spent frugally,

29:15.880 --> 29:17.400
it can last two or three years.

29:17.480 --> 29:19.600
Seems I still didn't calculate well.

29:21.560 --> 29:23.360
This matter of me selling essays,

29:23.440 --> 29:25.880
please keep it secret for me.
Don't tell anyone.

29:25.960 --> 29:26.920
Understood.

29:27.440 --> 29:28.720
I understand.

29:28.800 --> 29:30.080
I won't breathe a word.

29:32.200 --> 29:33.520
Changyu's lucky.

29:34.040 --> 29:36.200
She found a husband who can make money.

29:36.760 --> 29:40.560
Her hard days are over. She's blessed now.

29:59.600 --> 30:00.600
Changyu.

30:00.680 --> 30:01.640
Mrs. Zhao!

30:01.720 --> 30:03.160
Why did you come back so late?

30:04.040 --> 30:06.080
Come quickly and see
who's waiting for you.

30:06.160 --> 30:07.480
Mrs. Chen, you're here.

30:07.560 --> 30:09.000
Changyu.

30:11.120 --> 30:12.240
Open it and take a look.

30:15.400 --> 30:16.360
Come on. Open it.

30:35.000 --> 30:35.840
This…

30:37.400 --> 30:38.640
is mine?

30:40.240 --> 30:42.480
You said you'd only
make one for the groom.

30:43.320 --> 30:44.760
A girl's looks are important.

30:45.880 --> 30:47.600
I specifically saved some fabric

30:47.680 --> 30:49.360
and borrowed some scrap cloth.

30:49.440 --> 30:51.800
So, I made another set for you.

30:52.320 --> 30:54.120
-Thank you!
-With pleasure.

30:54.720 --> 30:56.120
So beautiful.

30:56.640 --> 30:58.280
-Look!
-Truly beautiful.

30:58.360 --> 30:59.600
So beautiful.

31:02.920 --> 31:04.160
What's this?

31:11.200 --> 31:12.960
What, don't you like it?

31:15.600 --> 31:16.880
I like it.

31:18.000 --> 31:20.680
But who's there to see
such beautiful embroidery?

31:21.960 --> 31:23.600
It's not for you to see.

31:25.960 --> 31:27.920
As long as your husband likes it,
that's fine.

31:28.000 --> 31:29.280
This is for him to wear?

31:32.000 --> 31:33.720
My silly girl.

31:34.840 --> 31:37.600
It's for you to wear
and show him on your wedding night.

31:42.320 --> 31:44.960
-Mrs. Zhao!
-Alright, alright.

32:01.480 --> 32:03.560
Boil beans, burn beanstalks.

32:04.160 --> 32:07.240
The beans in the pot cry out.

32:08.360 --> 32:10.000
We share the same father.

32:10.880 --> 32:13.200
Why torment each other?

32:16.240 --> 32:18.880
Boil beans, burn beanstalks.

32:21.280 --> 32:24.560
The beans in the pot cry out.

32:34.000 --> 32:36.960
-I shouldn't have hidden it under the bed.
-Boil beans, burn beanstalks.

32:37.480 --> 32:41.280
The beans in the pot cry out.

32:43.200 --> 32:45.440
We share the same father.

32:46.640 --> 32:48.960
Why torment each other?

32:55.360 --> 32:56.600
What are you doing here?

32:58.960 --> 33:01.640
You said yesterday to come
try on the wedding clothes.

33:05.200 --> 33:06.880
But our wedding clothes

33:07.400 --> 33:08.760
are all at Mrs. Zhao's place.

33:14.800 --> 33:16.480
Why is she sitting on the bed?

33:28.840 --> 33:30.680
Why is he also sitting over here?

33:38.080 --> 33:40.120
-Then let's go try them together.
-Okay.

33:43.760 --> 33:45.960
-Let's go together.
-Okay.

33:52.000 --> 33:53.920
-Go.
-Go.

33:54.000 --> 33:56.000
Why isn't he leaving yet?

33:56.520 --> 33:58.000
Has he seen it?

33:58.800 --> 34:01.200
Where's the box? Why can't I feel it?

34:02.120 --> 34:03.400
-Have you finished the poem?
-Have you finished your business?

34:03.480 --> 34:04.760
Have I finished…

34:05.880 --> 34:06.840
I…

34:07.440 --> 34:09.280
-Where was I?
-Share the same father…

34:12.960 --> 34:14.000
Born of the same root.

34:23.719 --> 34:25.120
Then I'll go first.

34:32.239 --> 34:33.639
She probably didn't see it.

34:44.040 --> 34:45.239
Better give it another day.

34:54.880 --> 34:55.880
He probably didn't see it.

34:55.960 --> 34:58.000
Definitely not, no, no.

35:00.000 --> 35:02.080
So embarrassing.

35:03.000 --> 35:04.280
What should I do?

35:07.880 --> 35:10.960
MARRIAGE

35:13.760 --> 35:16.640
HAVE A FULL MEAL

35:31.760 --> 35:33.320
So lively!

35:34.960 --> 35:37.080
Today is Changyu's wedding day.

35:37.160 --> 35:39.080
You need to fully remember the procedures.

35:39.160 --> 35:41.800
Don't worry. I know you're the expert.

35:41.880 --> 35:43.400
But today, you are the host.

35:43.480 --> 35:45.160
Relax and drink. I can handle this.

35:52.960 --> 35:54.920
You mean the live-in husband is very ugly?

35:55.000 --> 35:56.720
And also a cripple?

35:57.560 --> 35:58.720
If not ugly and lame,

35:58.800 --> 36:01.080
who would be a live-in husband these days?

36:01.160 --> 36:03.160
Kang, it's a joyous day.

36:03.240 --> 36:04.640
Watch your words.

36:04.720 --> 36:06.000
So much talk.

36:06.080 --> 36:06.960
Why is she here too?

36:07.560 --> 36:09.720
She's a distant relative of the Fans.
Nothing we can do.

36:10.600 --> 36:12.960
The Fan family's son-in-law comes forth!

36:21.360 --> 36:22.400
What did I say?

36:22.480 --> 36:24.960
Look, if he's not missing arms or legs,

36:25.040 --> 36:26.520
why would he be a live-in husband?

36:38.760 --> 36:40.840
I, Song Yan, have come to congratulate.

36:44.520 --> 36:45.440
Why are you here?

36:46.040 --> 36:46.880
Changyu.

36:47.520 --> 36:48.840
I'll give you one more chance.

36:49.560 --> 36:51.200
If you are willing to be my concubine,

36:51.280 --> 36:53.200
I will honor my vow and take you in.

36:53.720 --> 36:54.920
Take her as a concubine?

36:55.000 --> 36:56.560
This is so disrespectful.

36:56.640 --> 36:58.840
Are you deliberately trying
to humiliate Changyu?

36:58.920 --> 37:01.560
Exactly. Are you deliberately trying
to humiliate Changyu?

37:03.480 --> 37:05.920
This is the token of love Changyu gave me.

37:06.440 --> 37:08.240
There's nothing romantic between us now.

37:08.960 --> 37:11.080
So I should hand it over
to this live-in husband.

37:11.160 --> 37:13.360
I was only 6 years old
when I gave you these clay dolls.

37:13.440 --> 37:14.880
This isn't a token of love.

37:14.960 --> 37:16.840
You still remember it
from when you were 6.

37:16.920 --> 37:19.280
So you've never really put it behind you.

37:22.560 --> 37:23.840
Don't make me slap you.

37:23.920 --> 37:26.160
You're taking a husband.
I must come with a gift.

37:27.600 --> 37:29.040
Fan family's live-in husband,

37:29.120 --> 37:31.640
will you take this gift or not?

37:44.080 --> 37:45.560
Here he comes.

38:12.360 --> 38:13.400
Look at him.

38:13.480 --> 38:15.880
No wonder our Changyu said
she wasn't at a loss.

38:16.480 --> 38:19.960
Which blind person earlier
made up a story that the bridegroom

38:20.040 --> 38:22.520
was an ugly and deformed cripple?

38:22.600 --> 38:24.600
Wasn't it you, Kang?

38:26.120 --> 38:28.160
After all my years as a matchmaker,
I can tell you this.

38:28.240 --> 38:30.920
With looks like this, forget Song Yan.

38:31.000 --> 38:32.680
You won't find another in Lin'an Town.

38:32.760 --> 38:34.400
No, not in all of Qingping County.

38:34.480 --> 38:35.600
Yes.

38:38.800 --> 38:40.000
Are you taking this gift or not?

38:40.880 --> 38:42.000
I…

38:44.360 --> 38:45.200
accept.

38:51.960 --> 38:54.040
-I accept.
-Wait, accept what?

38:54.120 --> 38:56.360
I asked you to accept my token,
not to get married!

39:03.040 --> 39:04.360
One shouldn't be too kind.

39:04.880 --> 39:06.720
Aside from raising this ungrateful snake,

39:06.800 --> 39:09.040
you haven't raised
any other biting ones, have you?

39:12.000 --> 39:13.680
I've raised many livestock.

39:14.200 --> 39:15.720
This is the only one

39:15.800 --> 39:16.960
that bites back.

39:24.000 --> 39:25.200
Thank you

39:25.280 --> 39:27.240
for failing to recognize
gold inlaid with jade.

39:29.160 --> 39:30.280
Fan Changyu.

39:30.360 --> 39:31.960
I'll just assume you're infatuated.

39:32.040 --> 39:32.960
I won't hold it.

39:33.760 --> 39:35.160
Now I ask you one last time.

39:36.440 --> 39:37.600
Are you willing to be mine?

39:41.080 --> 39:41.760
You…

39:45.480 --> 39:46.320
Let's go.

39:47.480 --> 39:48.440
Alright.

39:48.960 --> 39:50.080
Listen.

39:50.160 --> 39:51.680
There will be a day you regret this!

39:53.880 --> 39:54.760
You…

39:56.440 --> 39:57.800
Hey!

39:57.880 --> 39:59.120
Keep it going!

39:59.200 --> 40:00.360
Fan Changyu, Yan Zheng,

40:00.440 --> 40:01.760
don't be too smug!

40:01.840 --> 40:03.280
Wait until I pass the exam.

40:03.360 --> 40:05.080
You'll get what's coming to you!

40:17.080 --> 40:18.440
Bow to the elders!

40:20.320 --> 40:21.480
Bow.

40:24.160 --> 40:28.800
MARRIAGE

40:30.960 --> 40:32.400
Share the bridal feast.

40:33.000 --> 40:35.360
From now on, share fortune and hardship,

40:35.440 --> 40:37.320
never leaving nor forsaking each other.

40:52.160 --> 40:53.560
Drink together.

40:56.760 --> 40:58.480
Rite of the Three Libations.

40:58.560 --> 41:00.560
Treat each other with courtesy.

41:03.960 --> 41:05.720
Drink from the joined nuptial cups.

41:05.800 --> 41:07.680
The wines mingle as one.

41:07.760 --> 41:10.240
Husband and wife forever in harmony.

41:21.920 --> 41:25.560
-Good.
-Good.

41:27.440 --> 41:28.520
Good!

41:29.920 --> 41:32.080
Husband and wife bow to each other.

41:48.960 --> 41:51.160
The grand wedding ceremony is complete.

41:51.680 --> 41:53.800
-Good!
-Good!

41:53.880 --> 41:55.480
Good!

41:55.560 --> 41:57.080
-Good!
-Good!

42:00.000 --> 42:02.680
Like before, a live-in husband
must change his surname.

42:03.280 --> 42:04.480
No need.

42:04.560 --> 42:06.560
My husband doesn't need
to change his surname.

42:06.640 --> 42:08.280
He'll remain Yan Zheng. It's a good name.

42:10.000 --> 42:11.840
When children are born,

42:11.920 --> 42:13.560
they need to follow the wife's surname.

42:14.160 --> 42:15.600
Th… that isn't necessary either.

42:15.680 --> 42:16.920
We will have several kids.

42:17.000 --> 42:18.480
They can have whichever surname.

42:22.240 --> 42:23.080
Continue.

42:23.160 --> 42:24.480
Get to the most important part.

42:25.480 --> 42:28.080
As a live-in husband, remember.
The wife holds authority.

42:28.160 --> 42:30.120
The woman is the head of the household.

42:30.200 --> 42:31.320
-The wife sets the rule,
-No.

42:31.400 --> 42:33.680
the husband obeys.

42:33.760 --> 42:35.880
-Good!
-No, no, no.

42:37.040 --> 42:38.200
From now on,

42:38.280 --> 42:39.800
I obey my wife's instructions.

42:40.680 --> 42:41.720
I comply with everything.

42:44.400 --> 42:45.440
If there are matters,

42:46.200 --> 42:48.320
we'll discuss together
and decide together.

42:49.120 --> 42:50.080
All right.

42:54.120 --> 42:55.240
What are we waiting for?

42:55.320 --> 42:56.840
Escort to the bridal chamber.

42:57.360 --> 42:58.640
Good!

42:58.720 --> 42:59.840
Come, Yan Zheng.

43:01.040 --> 43:02.000
Let's go, Yan Zheng.

43:04.800 --> 43:07.320
Our bride is here to toast everyone!

43:07.960 --> 43:09.560
Thank you. Thank you.

43:09.640 --> 43:10.600
-Thank you.
-Thank you.

43:10.680 --> 43:12.280
-Thank you all.
-Congratulations.

43:14.880 --> 43:17.240
The bride has come to toast.

43:17.320 --> 43:18.800
Changyu, congratulations.

43:19.400 --> 43:21.440
Everyone put in a lot of effort today,

43:21.520 --> 43:23.120
so make sure to eat and drink well.

43:23.720 --> 43:24.840
-Toast the bride!
-Come on.

43:24.920 --> 43:25.760
Come on.

43:25.840 --> 43:27.280
Come on.

44:02.480 --> 44:04.880
MEDICINE FOR WOUNDS

44:10.640 --> 44:12.720
Everyone, eat and drink well!

44:13.920 --> 44:15.200
Changyu.

44:15.280 --> 44:16.200
Changyu.

44:16.760 --> 44:18.040
Mr. Wang.

44:18.120 --> 44:19.840
Forgive me. I came late.

44:19.920 --> 44:21.000
Where were you?

44:21.960 --> 44:22.960
Changyu.

44:23.040 --> 44:24.760
I came late. Punish me with a drink.

44:27.800 --> 44:28.920
Quickly, quickly.

44:30.080 --> 44:31.280
Changyu.

44:31.360 --> 44:34.360
These days have been hard for you.

44:35.040 --> 44:36.520
I have seen it all.

44:36.600 --> 44:38.320
Your father and I were old friends.

44:38.400 --> 44:39.520
In the days to come,

44:40.120 --> 44:41.920
consider me as half a family

44:42.840 --> 44:44.800
and him as the other half.

44:47.640 --> 44:50.040
Changyu, I only hope

44:50.120 --> 44:52.160
the days ahead treat you kindly,

44:52.240 --> 44:54.240
that life keeps getting better,

44:54.320 --> 44:56.520
and that you and your husband
grow old together in love.

44:56.600 --> 44:58.280
-Good!
-Thank you, Mr. Wang.

44:58.880 --> 45:00.240
-Come, cheers!
-Cheers!

45:11.120 --> 45:12.600
Thank you all for today.

45:13.120 --> 45:14.080
You're welcome.

45:14.160 --> 45:15.720
Look at you. So pretty.

45:15.800 --> 45:16.800
Changyu is tired.

45:16.880 --> 45:17.920
Head back and rest.

45:18.000 --> 45:19.080
Alright. Safe travels.

45:19.160 --> 45:20.280
Congratulations, Changyu.

45:20.360 --> 45:22.160
-So beautiful.
-Rest early.

45:22.240 --> 45:23.080
Rest early.

45:33.200 --> 45:34.520
What are you doing?

45:34.600 --> 45:35.440
I'm washing dishes.

45:35.520 --> 45:36.680
Wait here.

45:37.280 --> 45:39.280
No need for you to wash.

45:41.560 --> 45:43.040
MANUAL OF THE BEDCHAMBER ARTS

45:48.080 --> 45:49.200
I don't need this.

45:49.280 --> 45:50.880
He's hurt like that.
We won't be needing it.

45:50.960 --> 45:52.720
Soon enough you will.

45:52.800 --> 45:54.160
Back to the bridal chamber.

45:54.240 --> 45:55.520
I'll do the dishes.

45:55.600 --> 45:56.880
Let me do it. You go.

45:57.480 --> 45:59.160
Don't get in the way. Hurry up.

46:03.160 --> 46:04.520
-Changyu.
-Changyu.

46:04.600 --> 46:05.440
Upstairs, quickly.

46:06.040 --> 46:08.800
Every minute of the wedding night
is precious.

46:09.840 --> 46:11.200
Go on.

46:13.760 --> 46:15.960
Alright, go quickly.

46:23.200 --> 46:24.280
Wait.

46:28.120 --> 46:29.320
Sorry.

46:32.120 --> 46:33.080
I'm used to living alone.

46:33.160 --> 46:34.880
I keep forgetting there's a man here now.

49:12.800 --> 49:16.520
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
IN THE MAKING OF THIS EPISODE

